      QA('Name the four essential elements of the State.',
          '1. Population - the people living in the state. 2. Territory - a definite area of land. 3. Government - the machinery that makes and enforces laws. 4. Sovereignty - supreme authority over all persons and associations within, and freedom from outside control.'),
